Microinstructions and other info for the Bubble Bobble-machine.
By Natanael Log

** Different bus slots on the machine **
** (t) meaning "writes to bus"
** (f) meaning "reads from bus"
** (t/f) meaning "writes and reads from bus"

   000 : nothing...
   001 : IR (t/f)
   010 : PM (t/f)
   011 : PC (t/f)
   100 : AR (t)
   101 : nothing...
   110 : GR (t/f)
   111 : AR (f)
